reviewText: it was quite interesting to me, however when my son asked me to order it to complete collection, for my 4 year old grandson, I did not know it was an actual movie. My grandson wants to watch it, but loses interest easily
it's fun to watch the 1st 2 VCDs as we can see many funny scenes, but it doesn't encourage me to see thh 3rd VCD since I believe they're all similar.
